&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THIS POST IS FIXED TERM FOR 6 MONTHS DUE TO MEET THE NEEDS OF THE SERVICE. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen to support the Porter Security Team within Porter Services at Royal Glamorgan Hospital Site. The position will involve supporting the Porter Services Supervisor and Porter Team Leader in supervising the provision of Porter and security services delivery that are managed from a Facilities Control Centre based at the hospital and ensuring a high quality service is delivered to patients, staff and visitors in accordance with service specifications. Post holder will be required to perform supplementary duties to respond to service needs and that are appropriate to the Facilities services and in line with their grade.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The position will support full time position and will be operational with a rota across seven days weekly including both days, afternoons and nights shifts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing Date: 08/11/2020 &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Lisa Rogers&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Facilities Operational Site Manager&lt;/p&gt;
